[
    {
        "text": "So, let's say you save your quarters in a piggy bank...",
        "startTime": 399,
        "endTime": 2267,
        "slowStartTime": 749,
        "slowEndTime": 3625
    },
    {
        "text": "...that you keep on a shelf in your room.",
        "startTime": 2358,
        "endTime": 3767,
        "slowStartTime": 3687,
        "slowEndTime": 5875
    },
    {
        "text": "But your mom keeps checking up on how much you're putting in...",
        "startTime": 4244,
        "endTime": 6538,
        "slowStartTime": 6516,
        "slowEndTime": 10032
    },
    {
        "text": "...and how much you're taking out.",
        "startTime": 6613,
        "endTime": 7739,
        "slowStartTime": 10069,
        "slowEndTime": 11833
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't like that, so what you need is a second piggy bank...",
        "startTime": 7955,
        "endTime": 10398,
        "slowStartTime": 12083,
        "slowEndTime": 15822
    },
    {
        "text": "...that you keep somewhere else.",
        "startTime": 10490,
        "endTime": 11675,
        "slowStartTime": 15885,
        "slowEndTime": 17737
    },
    {
        "text": "Your friend Johnny's mom is busy. She doesn't have time to check on piggy banks.",
        "startTime": 11952,
        "endTime": 15469,
        "slowStartTime": 18078,
        "slowEndTime": 23429
    },
    {
        "text": "You can bring a spare bank over there,...",
        "startTime": 15812,
        "endTime": 17439,
        "slowStartTime": 23868,
        "slowEndTime": 26383
    },
    {
        "text": "...then money can come and go without anyone being the wiser.",
        "startTime": 17532,
        "endTime": 20156,
        "slowStartTime": 26448,
        "slowEndTime": 30459
    },
    {
        "text": "But maybe Johnny's mom isn't really too busy.",
        "startTime": 20627,
        "endTime": 22848,
        "slowStartTime": 31090,
        "slowEndTime": 34497
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe she's just lazy.",
        "startTime": 23141,
        "endTime": 24072,
        "slowStartTime": 34861,
        "slowEndTime": 36333
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe she's deliberately telling the whole neighborhood that, for a small fee,...",
        "startTime": 24251,
        "endTime": 27533,
        "slowStartTime": 36527,
        "slowEndTime": 41524
    },
    {
        "text": "...she'll keep their piggy banks safe and not pay attention to what happens.",
        "startTime": 27775,
        "endTime": 30939,
        "slowStartTime": 41813,
        "slowEndTime": 46634
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what countries like Panama and the Cayman Islands and other tax havens do.",
        "startTime": 31359,
        "endTime": 34867,
        "slowStartTime": 47188,
        "slowEndTime": 52526
    },
    {
        "text": "They have very weak regulations in terms of watching...",
        "startTime": 35259,
        "endTime": 37776,
        "slowStartTime": 53039,
        "slowEndTime": 56889
    },
    {
        "text": "...when money comes in or out of bank accounts...",
        "startTime": 37884,
        "endTime": 39737,
        "slowStartTime": 56976,
        "slowEndTime": 59830
    },
    {
        "text": "...and they have rules that make it easy to form a corporation without disclosing who owns it.",
        "startTime": 40068,
        "endTime": 44321,
        "slowStartTime": 60252,
        "slowEndTime": 66706
    },
    {
        "text": "So basically, everyone gets to write a fake name on their piggy bank.",
        "startTime": 44617,
        "endTime": 47354,
        "slowStartTime": 67075,
        "slowEndTime": 71256
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a Panamanian law firm called Mossack Fonseca.",
        "startTime": 47806,
        "endTime": 50515,
        "slowStartTime": 71859,
        "slowEndTime": 75997
    },
    {
        "text": "They've got over 40 offices in dozens of countries around the world.",
        "startTime": 50653,
        "endTime": 53792,
        "slowStartTime": 76130,
        "slowEndTime": 80913
    },
    {
        "text": "They specialize in setting up this kind of special piggy banks.",
        "startTime": 54069,
        "endTime": 56867,
        "slowStartTime": 81254,
        "slowEndTime": 85526
    },
    {
        "text": "They're called \"shell companies,\"...",
        "startTime": 56999,
        "endTime": 58415,
        "slowStartTime": 85649,
        "slowEndTime": 87848
    },
    {
        "text": "...hollow vessels that don't conduct any business.",
        "startTime": 58541,
        "endTime": 60845,
        "slowStartTime": 87962,
        "slowEndTime": 91492
    },
    {
        "text": "They just own financial assets on behalf of their real owners.",
        "startTime": 61029,
        "endTime": 64248,
        "slowStartTime": 91694,
        "slowEndTime": 96597
    },
    {
        "text": "There's been this massive leak of over two terabytes worth of Mossack Fonseca documents...",
        "startTime": 64441,
        "endTime": 68725,
        "slowStartTime": 96811,
        "slowEndTime": 103313
    },
    {
        "text": "...to the International Consortium of Investigative Journalists.",
        "startTime": 69038,
        "endTime": 71695,
        "slowStartTime": 103707,
        "slowEndTime": 107767
    },
    {
        "text": "And it sheds an unprecedented light on the world of shell companies.",
        "startTime": 71785,
        "endTime": 74813,
        "slowStartTime": 107827,
        "slowEndTime": 112444
    },
    {
        "text": "People can use these shell companies for legitimate reasons.",
        "startTime": 75332,
        "endTime": 77753,
        "slowStartTime": 113148,
        "slowEndTime": 116854
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes you just need privacy...",
        "startTime": 77854,
        "endTime": 79352,
        "slowStartTime": 116931,
        "slowEndTime": 119253
    },
    {
        "text": "...but they're also really useful for covering up scandalous or embarrassing information.",
        "startTime": 79537,
        "endTime": 83635,
        "slowStartTime": 119455,
        "slowEndTime": 125678
    }
]